snippet.title: Does It Stack? - Official Meta Quest Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Check out the wholesome trailer for Does It Stack? as the physics-based VR puzzle game gets a release window for Meta Quest. Craft increasingly absurd towers that joyfully defy the laws of physics using a treasure trove of wonky stuff. Does It Stack? will be available on Meta Quest in fall 2024, and it is already available on Steam.
